{"build_type":"library","description":"Lower an invoke_computed_address high instruction into native low-ops. Mirrors lower_function_invocation_to_native_ops but the call target is a RUNTIME ADDRESS held in a local variable instead of a static name: it declares the result local, builds the call-argument array by REUSING lower_function_invocation_to_native_ops_loop1 (DRY arg-setup via the shared g_lowering_ops_ptr global), then emits a call_indirect low-op carrying the address variable name (rendered as mov rax,[slot] + FF D0) plus args and dest. No fixup is recorded because the target is a value, not a symbol.","module_name":"lower-invoke-computed-address-towards-native-operations","package_name":"lower-invoke-computed-address-towards-native-operations","function_definitions":{"lower-invoke-computed-address-towards-native-operations":{"return_type":"void","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"inst","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"ops","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_result_assignment_variable","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"result_assignment_variable"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_local","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"local"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_name","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"name"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_invocation_arguments","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"invocation_arguments"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_dest","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"dest"},{"instruction_type":"variable_decla